{"tid":31784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環球時報：蕭若元是走資派的最終兵器","createTime":"2016-12-10T00:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T03:03:26.000Z","uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e795836a67adb83fe2313aaa620b62880d95aef3","tid":31784,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f4337943c04637e92ac768500d8720ebd7be3c","tid":31784,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:17:10.000Z","msg":"燈力先係佢最強嘅地方"},{"pid":"bf3adaaaae608bea68897fffcf08fe49da919544","tid":31784,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:44:31.000Z","msg":"老蕭認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4ff1a6e1750f866b41c6a25b99d7fd797eafc5","tid":31784,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老蕭認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我們在香港的燈神，<br />\n<br />\n願人都尊燒山的名為燈；<br />\n<br />\n願燒山的國降臨；<br />\n<br />\n願燒山的旨意行在地上，<br />\n<br />\n如同行在最新燒析。<br />\n<br />\n我們日用的人網幣，<br />\n<br />\n求燒山今日賜給我們。<br />\n<br />\n又求饒恕我們的假膠，<br />\n<br />\n因為我們饒恕得罪燒山的人。<br />\n<br />\n不叫我們遇見試探，<br />\n<br />\n拯救我們脫離港共。<br />\n<br />\n因為國度、權柄、榮耀、<br />\n<br />\n全是燒山的，直到永遠。膠們。"}]}